{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/the-heart-fragile-as-glass/","result":{"data":{"thePost":{"date":"2009-11-02T12:43:00","databaseId":833,"content":"\n<div class=WordSection1>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Michelle Nass<br>\n<br>\nEnglish 10 Honors<br>\n<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The heart&#8230; fragile as glass<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Protected just as easily as it is exposed<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Longing to love&#8230; willing to risk\neverything<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The end comes&#8230; a test<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Shattering and building the heart<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Building wisdom with experience<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>And<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Shattering&#8230; the heart thinks it never\nwill be pieced back together<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>But it will, undoubtedly, be fixed<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Our heart looks to find love<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>This is what we have been created for<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Because we are drawn to love<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>We are filled with emotion<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>What we do not know how to express<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>What we know how to express<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>We look into the future<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The perfect future<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Without mistake<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Without sin, yet<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>As humans, we cannot live perfectly<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The future holds nothing we can truly\npredict<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>For the future, is mystery<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>We become blinded by infatuation<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>And believe we have found perfection<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Perhaps we have<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Riding the wings of life<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The wings that carry<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>And fill us with emotion and experience<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>All must ride this phoenix<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>To truly experience life<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>The future holds many things<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Untold greatness will come out of it<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Great evil will arise before the end<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>And then final, complete perfection<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Something this universe has never held\nbefore<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>It will last<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif'>Will you last?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n","title":"The heart… fragile as glass","author":{"node":{"name":"Jacob Stephens"}},"categories":{"nodes":[{"link":"/posts/category/literature/","name":"Literature"}]},"tags":{"nodes":[]},"featuredImage":null},"nextPost":{"title":"Socialism, capitalism, and demand elasticity","uri":"/posts/socialism-capitalism-and-demand-elasticity/"},"prevPost":{"title":"Apart from the norm: Huxley argued for individualism through Brave New World","uri":"/posts/apart-from-the-norm/"}},"pageContext":{"databaseId":833,"nextId":504,"prevId":836}},"staticQueryHashes":["2089240339","3862348194","63159454"]}